snippet.title: Desperados III - Money for the Vultures Part 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
Desperados III - Money for the Vultures Part 2: Five Steps Ahead is OUT NOW.

In the second part of Money for the Vultures, the gang returns to Louisiana to challenge a new member of the DeVitt family. Explore a brand new location in the Bayou State, reunite with Isabelle for more Voodoo shenanigans and face off against a mastermind worthy of your talents.
---
Website: http://desperadosgame.com
Discord: http://discord.gg/desperados
